SECURE QUERYING PROTOCOL,0.10995850622406639,"Secure prediction. Recently, many works achieve secure prediction protocols in client-server set-
ting (i.e., 2-party setting), such as the SOTA CrypTFlow2 (Rathee et al., 2020) or HE-Transformer"
