REFERENCES,0.6244813278008299,"Impact of the coefﬁcient λ in mixup. Table 5 shows the impact of different mixup coefﬁcients
λ on the model accuracy over CIFAR10. For each result, we only use one coefﬁcient to generate
synthetic images. We can observe that in different coefﬁcient values, the model accuracy remains
almost unchanged, and hence the coefﬁcient of mixup has a negligible effect on the accuracy of the
heterogeneous models in PrivHFL. Therefore, we set λ ∈[0.1, 0.9] with an interval of 0.1 in our
experiments to generate more diverse synthetic images."
