REFERENCES,0.7012448132780082,"Therefore, they need to ﬁrst construct a big unlabeled data pool based on the small number of pri-
vate data, and then actively choose a subset from the pool as the query data in each iteration. Next,
they perform the secure querying protocol based on the query data, and obtains the ﬁnal predictions,
which will be used to retrain the local model. Query-data generation and secure querying process
